OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,FShe has launched a petition, urging
OL,8,Fthe government to better regulate e-
OL,9,Fscooters. She wants e-scooters to be
OL,10,Fillegal for anyone under the age of 18
OL,11,Fto ride and anyone without a driving
OL,12,Flicense.
OL,14,FCarly said "people are going to use
OL,15,Fthese e-scooters no matter what." So
OL,16,Fshe wants the government to make
OL,17,Fscooters safer.
OL,26,@vD@LOUwD@aO]
