OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,FHer petition calls for mandatory
OL,8,Fhelmets and a ban on carrying
OL,9,Fpassengers. She asks for stricter
OL,10,Fpunishments for those breaching the
OL,11,Flaws.
OL,13,FCarly's petition currently sits at
OL,14,F26,000 signatures, but it needs
OL,15,F100,000 by 18 December to be debated
OL,16,Fin parliament.
OL,18,F"I think Jacob would be really proud
OL,19,Fof me."
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@GO]
