OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,F"That's what keeps me going on a daily
OL,8,Fbasis. I'm using my pain as his power
OL,9,Fand I'm pushing out there to stop
OL,10,Fother people going through what I'm
OL,11,Fgoing through."
OL,13,F"He may have lost his life but
OL,14,Fhopefully he's saving thousands more."
OL,16,FCarly described Jacob as a "cheeky
OL,17,Fchappy", mischievous and funny. The 14-
OL,18,Fyear-old loved gaming and Manchester
OL,19,FUnited, and dreamed of travelling the
OL,20,Fworld one day.
