OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,FHis mum Carly still feels like he's
OL,8,Fgoing to come home. "I'm broken. It's
OL,9,Freally hard. Jacob's toothbrush is
OL,10,Fstill upstairs, his noodles are still
OL,11,Fin the cupboard. He's around me, he's
OL,12,Feverywhere I look."
OL,14,FAccording to a Parliamentary Advisory
OL,15,FGroup, there have been 59 deaths from
OL,16,Fe-scooter accidents in the UK since
OL,17,F2019. The youngest rider was just nine-
OL,18,Fyears-old.
