OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,FCarly is drawing attention to these
OL,8,Fnumbers through her _NoEmptyChairs
OL,9,Fcampaign.
OL,11,FThe video she's created shows photos
OL,12,Fof Jacob over the years at Christmas
OL,13,Fending with a photo of him in
OL,14,Fintensive care, and his funeral.
OL,16,FThe text reads: "If you buy your child
OL,17,Fan e-scooter this Christmas, it may
OL,18,Fmean an empty chair next Christmas, in
OL,19,Fyour home or someone else's."
