OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,FCarly didn't buy Jacob an e-scooter,
OL,8,Fcausing arguments with her son. But
OL,9,Fstill he rode on the back of his
OL,10,Ffriend's scooter, another 14-year-old
OL,11,Fboy who suffered minor injuries from
OL,12,Fthe crash.
OL,14,F"Imagine buying your child that for
OL,15,FChristmas day and they go out and have
OL,16,Fan accident. How would you feel?
OL,17,FBecause I feel it and I didn't buy
OL,18,FJacob that e-scooter," she said.
